My own config files.

Debian dependency list:
$ sudo apt-get install awesome feh conky firefox emacs lxterminal audacious thunar hunspell gpicview redshift


In order to add emerge as mergetool run:
$ git config --global merge.tool emerge
$ git config --global mergetool.emerge.path $HOME/.emacs.d/emerge-for-git

Fancy pants git log
git config --global alias.lg "log --color --graph --pretty=format:'%Cred%h%Creset -%C(yellow)%d%Creset %s %Cgreen(%cr)%C(bold blue)<%an>%Creset' --abbrev-commit"